### Config-Driven Deployment - Complete E-Commerce API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. List Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

### 3. Get Product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1

### 4. Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Smith",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123"
}

### 5. Register User - Password Too Short (validation error)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob Jones",
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "password": "123"
}

### 6. Get User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/user-123

### 7. Create Order (triggers DB, Cache, Email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-123",
  "product_id": "1",
  "quantity": 2
}

### 8. Create Order - Below Minimum (validation error)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-123",
  "product_id": "2",
  "quantity": 1
}

### 9. Multiple Orders Test
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "user-456",
  "product_id": "3",
